Rise Up by Stargate features Nelson Mandela’s prominent speech. This track is part of the Global Citizen EP. The Global Citizen Festival: Mandela 100 was celebrated at the FNB Stadium, Johannesburg, South Africa.  On the 2nd of December, there were musical performances from Beyoncé & JAY-Z, Cassper Nyovest, D’banj, Ed Sheeran, Eddie Vedder, Kacey Musgraves, Femi Kuti, Pharrell Williams & Chris Martin, Sho Madjozi, Tiwa Savage, Usher, and Wizkid in honour of Mandela.